longBusinessSummary: NGS Group AB (publ) provides recruitment and staffing services in Sweden, Norway, and Finland. It focuses on care, school, social services, finance, regulatory services, and executive search in private and public sectors. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
